  "detailed_description": "Prepare to be blown away! Jiangshi x Daoshi is an epic story of Chinese vampires, dao priests, assassins and immortals, told in a spectacularly animated visual novel format.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338460/extras/255e4206ed11e362ddb423f27c1474d8.poster.avif?t=1743588530\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338460/extras/255e4206ed11e362ddb423f27c1474d8.webm?t=1743588530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338460/extras/255e4206ed11e362ddb423f27c1474d8.mp4?t=1743588530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>When former assassin Luan is attacked by man-eating creatures, he is saved from certain death by a wandering dao priest, Ling Ling. At that time, neither of them know what tribulations yet await them.</i><br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Breathtakingly animated action<br></li><li>Explosions that cut mountains in half<br></li><li>Sexy assassins of both sexes<br></li><li>Blood, gore and humor</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338460/extras/1075ded0d71c38722d3ef0b211490807.poster.avif?t=1743588530\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338460/extras/1075ded0d71c38722d3ef0b211490807.webm?t=1743588530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338460/extras/1075ded0d71c38722d3ef0b211490807.mp4?t=1743588530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Includes Jiangshi x Daoshi Episode I - Boy Meets Girl, and Episode II - The Fable of the Fake Elixir of Life.</strong><br><br><i>Not for the faint of heart - you have been warned!</i>",
